dct_title_s: Croatia city graphic 1:12,000. Slavonski Brod. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Slavonski Brod. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 10 meter contour intervals and spot elevation. Coordinate conversion WGS 84 to ED 50. This sheet falls within NL 33-9 and NL 34-7, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2785 III, M709, 1:50,000. Relief shown by contour lines and spot elevation. "Map information as of 1995. Compiled in 1996 from best available sources" On left lower margin: WGZ 84.
